{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"da6421b6eb","title":"在“百花学社”成立大会上的发言","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"953df56fd0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"da6421b6eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"b1a23c6fa5","name":"杨路"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d6f5012759","type":"title","text":"在“百花学社”成立大会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"79b80f4b9e","type":"authors","text":"北京大学杨路","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"4af57cd929","type":"subtitle","text":"（杨路：北京大学数学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"116eaf558b","type":"paragraph","text":"十天中，我校运动是民主运动——扩大社会主义民主和社会主义法制有它自下而上的一方面，这运动是符合党的利益的，党中央是同情的。目前民主运动已处于沉静状态。根本原因是感情高潮已过去了。自由空气的形成，自由权利的获得是十天来的主要成绩。林希翎对造成自由讨论的空气很有帮助。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"817b66f22f","type":"paragraph","text":"本社团是为了作学术性的讨论而成立的。我们要学习哲学书籍，多思维，可以进行一些讨论。如林希翎提出的一些理论问题。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"4803659d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"以后要继续揭发各种错误。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"0b5bd38386","type":"paragraph","text":"对外宣传可以，反对对廿九人的指责。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"93811f9dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"刘奇弟在胡风问题上收兵可以，因为已经提出了问题。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"6e5ca35536","type":"paragraph","text":"刊物要发行到各大学。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"},{"id":"a1f76d1637","type":"paragraph","text":"我是唯心主义者，但真正的共产主义者是应该同意我们的。  (完)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb"}],"page":{"id":"2a4c7d1b15","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da6421b6eb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}